item.title: CVE-2023-28045|2023-05-19T08:35:58.535Z -- dell -- cloudiq%20collector
item.description: Dell CloudIQ Collector version 1.10.2 contains a missing encryption of sensitive data vulnerability. An attacker with low privileges could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to gain access to unauthorized data.
